query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('english')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('adverbs',
'antonyms',
'articles',
'british-english',
'phrase-meaning',
'pronunciation',
'punctuation',
'slang',
'syntactic-analysis',
'tenses',
'usage',
'verb-agreement',
'word-order',
'writing-style');
